'''Chume Ta' ''' was a [[Hapan]] designator that formed part of [[Tenel Ka Djo|Tenel Ka's]] full name of "Tenel Ka Chume Ta' Djo". Rather than a personal name, however, it may have been a Hapan title given to the firstborn daughter of the current [[Queen Mother]].

